title: #155 - Belle Delphine Shocks Us & Trisha Paytas' Fake Wedding
description:
On this episode of The H3 Podcast we talk about the generosity of Turkish chefs, review podcast memes, check out a wild wiping tutorial, review Matthew McConaughey's Instagram debut, check in with our old friend Shoenice, rank a bunch of the candies we missed on the last episode, watch Belle's weird new video, and a WHOLE lot more!
  
 Czn gives the gift of mobility: https://www.instagram.com/p/B4fMMAnHplk/?igshid=2udj13wb77gn
  
 Girl gets interviewed about regulating scooter speed: https://youtu.be/vG8X7N6Kwv0
  
 Trisha got married: https://youtu.be/sGhBcXkn9B8
  
 Meme album: https://imgur.com/a/WylgJMX
  
 McConaughey joins Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/p/B4cww3Jg3C-/?igshid=t9c7sd6hhqoi
  
 Shoenice: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aBFTslMKUrQ
  
 Belle Delphine is back: https://youtu.be/iY27pp3vnrA
